            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "一件不留！︱貴州超市「執笠」清貨  逾500購物車被偷走",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a722c5f3806280bb814881f594077a76/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041610194780183.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>貴州有超市「執笠」，大減價要錢唔要貨，不過民眾將「清貨」當「任攞」，竟連店方的大型購物車也帶回家，令超市逾500輛手推車被一掃光，最終要報警處理。\n\n</p><h2>暫僅追回30多輛</h2>\n<p>據《新京報》報道，永輝超市在貴州貴陽花果園大街的分店結業，早前舉行清貨大減價，吸引大量民眾前往執平貨。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4ac0197b15c417ade032c547b006bd8/2025-04/55_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b61aa85ad4152e9a088cb605f41bdb9f/2025-04/4156456.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"永輝超市指已就購物車被偷一事報警。微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6b1a219d66a7043bdf9d678c0ed80220/2025-04/5265665.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        永輝超市指已就購物車被偷一事報警。微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/25b3d76142536a7f478357341f5b8834/2025-04/12312633.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/751c73ccb3de1cf4b70507e6740d0b7e/2025-04/12352323.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a641e9e8d43344dfe68bc678cf25e9a8/2025-04/154156562.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貴州有超市結業前清貨，店內逾500輛購物車遭居民偷走。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>民眾疑囤貨太多，居然有很多人順手將超市的購物車載著貨品推回家，令超市原本有逾500輛的購物車，漸漸歸零。\n\n</p>\n<p>貴州永輝超市14日發公告，指花果園大街店在清貨期間，丟失逾500輛購物車，經查看閉路電視，發現皆為附近居民每日購物時推走未歸還。由於數量多且價值高，已報警處理。\n\n</p>\n<p>公告呼籲「順手推車」的居民盡快歸還購物車。\n\n</p>\n<p>大皖新聞報道，永輝超市工作人員官先生14日表示，物管公司在周邊排查後，已追回30多輛購物車，針對此次購物車丟失事件，已第一時間報警並積極配合警方調查。同時，呼籲廣大市民共同維護公共設施。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
