        {
            "title": "有片｜牛池灣綠Van泊路邊溜後撞貨車 司機救車不果變「滾地葫蘆」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/7208b4e02eaf3e8f57cc8a0e01bffe53/2025-04/FotoJet_5.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/a0cd428c1a6671f090654177d1c10102/96c4b4edf50d43c58e2296cd01ae1aec-67e3ff5c81e4bfc25d4683cb05457720-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ff0ff391a97\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ff0ff391a99\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a86eca5c82d1a9039a3a843d16f9ea3b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041610013186684.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>牛池灣有綠色小巴溜後撞貨車。今日（16日）網上流出一段車Cam影片，顯示昨日早上約11時，一輛綠Van亮起死火燈，停泊在牛池灣街斜路路邊，司機已落車離開小巴。惟期間綠Van突然溜後，身處小巴前方的男司機見狀，連忙奔向綠Van並打開打司機位車門試圖「救車」，但不果整個人被拖跌倒地。綠Van繼續溜後，直撞後方的貨車才停下。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197630/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c086a21aa655f5b5e47bc6b405aadbaf/2025-04/1_0_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197631/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0582cb52fe14dbddfa898a6cd173474d/2025-04/2_0_12.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197632/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/119db8134f098eeffe336bc704f0fad5/2025-04/3_27.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197633/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cd71cba87393c450f75704ced1fb110/2025-04/4_29.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197634/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1dd0bc38a96280afca9110a3e347ef47/2025-04/5_23.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>事發時有數名踏單車車友經過沿路上斜，他們見狀後亦停車回望，幸片尾可見綠Van司機可自行爬起身。網民質疑司機未拉妥手掣便下車，「都唔明點解冇拉手掣都夠膽落車」、「冇拉手掣佢一落車嗰下就已經溜咗落嚟，應該係手掣拉唔實或者有問題」，又指「明知斜路 棍頭就入個波啦」、「好彩有架大車頂住」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197635/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5fc2159eaa4b4157fa8330a6ca4cf43b/2025-04/6_0_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197636/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03677da18c7c1b3c6c958ee116db0f1d/2025-04/7_19.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197637/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/23abc9ff93fde497fe0879b236842dc0/2025-04/8_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197638/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/333c60d09952ffbfaa174bdff54a4fad/2025-04/9_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197639/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1662bda948d32baddc5c42cd23a6823a/2025-04/10_8.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4197640/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/195392df7052416b2825884a1949b713/2025-04/11_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方在昨日早上11時03分接報，事件中綠van溜後並撞倒一輛中型貨車及4米欄杆，72歲男司機沒有受傷，案件列作交通意外無人受傷及財物損毀處理。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064189/即時-港聞-有片-牛池灣綠Van泊路邊溜後撞貨車-司機救車不果變-滾地葫蘆",
