            "title": "歐聯｜巴塞吞2025年首敗不敵多蒙特 但仍隔6年再入4強 費歷克：今場要反省",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d65b3bc0f2676678b90273935bd8daa5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041609582756831.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>巴塞隆拿於周二歐聯8蛋次回合作客1:3不敵多蒙特，但仍以總比數5:3淘汰後者，事隔6年後重返4強。不過，巴塞吞下踏入2025年後首敗，故主帥費歷克賽後直言要好好反省一下。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e9deb2064fdbc871487eb935bea0d204/2025-04/2025-04-15T201910Z_506166279_UP1EL4F1KFWP9_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3f938a72fe44871ec7e9583f694cd19/2025-04/2025-04-15T210710Z_217835181_UP1EL4F1MNXSO_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/387fc9af11035c75db6e1fbb3acc8baa/2025-04/2025-04-15T210723Z_808770347_UP1EL4F1MO9SP_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿事隔6年再入4強。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古拉斯(黃衫)今場入3球。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/90778e89a6d1e1568afb716b1b521260/2025-04/2025-04-15T190922Z_844529049_UP1EL4F1H7KLC_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古拉斯(黃衫)今場入3球。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ac62bf3eddebe9ca7134f9151ecdcd52/2025-04/2025-04-15T203815Z_298844615_UP1EL4F1LBQQH_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c4213a128ceccc7fe68edda07c82a76/2025-04/2025-04-15T202842Z_808122029_UP1EL4F1KVRQ0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9455a7f405f93a1762987e70842e19cc/2025-04/2025-04-15T201501Z_1713635392_UP1EL4F1K90OW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2aafe1a1c4861c2db935f772626726bd/2025-04/2025-04-15T210752Z_1359135077_UP1EL4F1MP2SQ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-BVB-BAR-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        多蒙特贏波也要出局。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>巴塞隔6年再入4強</h2>\n<p>多蒙特首回合落後0:4，今場回到主場即用10分鐘就開紀錄，由古拉斯射入12碼，半場領先1球。換邊後4分鐘，多蒙特角球攻勢，古拉斯接應二傳門前頂入成2:0，將總比數拉近至2:4。54分鐘，多蒙特的賓斯拜尼誤擺烏龍，總比數再被拉開。雖然古拉斯之後完成帽子戲法助多蒙特贏3:1，但返魂乏術總比數輸3:5，而巴塞就自2019年後再入歐聯4強。\n\n</p><h2>巴塞吞2025年首敗</h2>\n<p>巴塞自踏入2025年後走勢強勁，於各賽事24場不敗。另外，門將施捷斯尼今季22次出任球隊正選時亦不敗，不過今次輸波就令兩項紀錄同時被打破。\n\n</p><h2>費歷克：要反省</h2>\n<p>巴塞主帥費歷克賽後直言：「我們需要分析這場比賽，需要看看球隊有哪些方面可以提高和改善，研究一下是甚麼東西影響了我們的表現，然後專注於下場比賽。」不過對於晉級他也高興道：「也許我們可以踢得更好，但我們的目標就是晉級4強，所以今天會好好慶祝。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
